"{\"uid\": \"rappler.com-sports-updates-results-highlights-team-philippines-paris-olympics-august-4-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  SUMMARY  This is AI generated summarization, which may have errors.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 69, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 21, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9961768925840496, \"rank\": 0.0038371769993072236, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For context, always refer to the full article.\", \"from\": 70, \"to\": 116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"MANILA, Philippines - Team Philippines finally barged into themedal tallyof the Paris Olympics courtesy of gymnastics heroCarlos Yulo, and there is hope for more precious hardware on Sunday, August 4.\", \"from\": 118, \"to\": 318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 126, \"end\": 137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.9984839826374747, \"rank\": 0.0015182298100750587, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}, {\"begin\": 145, \"end\": 156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.9984839826374747, \"rank\": 0.0015182298100750587, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here is Team Philippines' schedule (Manila time):  Carlos Yulo makes history anew as he becomes the Philippines' first double Olympic gold medalist after reigning in the men's artistic gymnastics vault final in the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 320, \"to\": 547, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 356, \"end\": 362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\", \"score\": 0.9998468750782